			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>I used splitters and only powered 3 of the 6 cards on my six card configurations. With such low power usage, running three 270(x) cards isn&#8217;t going to strain your motherboard. I&#8217;d recommend getting a 750 PSU and run it alongside your 850 watt one with an add2psu adapter.</p>
